  "text": "Lastly, the high levels of Clk mRNA in Clk Jrk and cyc 01 flies suggest that Clk is constitutively activated. As ectopic expression of Clk is capable of inducing circadian clock function [CITATION_1] , it is possible that the constitutive activator is the same one that activates Clk during development. Characterizing Clk developmental expression and regulation might be a profitable way to resolve this question.",
